title: Daniel Boone, Trail Blazer (1956 Western) Lon Chaney Jr., Bruce Bennett

sources.title: Daniel Boone, Trail Blazer (1956 Western) Lon Chaney Jr., Bruce Bennett
sources.description:
Daniel Boone leads settlers into Kentucky, but must battle Shawnee Indians who have been persuaded by a French renegade that Boone and the settlers are there to kill them and steal their land.

Directors: Albert C. Gannaway, Ismael Rodríguez
Writers: Tom Hubbard, John Patrick

Main cast:
Bruce Bennett - Daniel Boone
Lon Chaney Jr. - Blackfish
Faron Young - Faron Callaway
Kem Dibbs - Simon Girty
Damian O'Flynn - Andy Callaway
Jacqueline Evans - Rebecca Boone
Nancy Rodman - Susannah Boone
Freddy Fernández - Israel Boone
Carol Kelly - Jemima Boone
Eduardo Noriega - Squire Boone

Genres: Action, Drama, History, Western
Release date: October 5, 1956
Filming location: Mexico
